WEBVTT

00:01:28.360 --> 00:01:31.560
Given the current situation,
it sounds impossible,

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:35.880
but humanity already knows what to do.

00:01:37.160 --> 00:01:40.736
We have real, workable
technologies and practices

00:01:40.760 --> 00:01:42.200
that can achieve drawdown.

00:01:43.480 --> 00:01:44.766
And it's already happening.

00:01:45.760 --> 00:01:49.856
What we need is
to accelerate implementation

00:01:49.880 --> 00:01:51.896
and to change the discourse

00:01:51.920 --> 00:01:56.400
from one of fear and confusion,
which only leads to apathy,

00:01:57.720 --> 00:02:01.336
to one of understanding and possibility,